@startuml
skinparam maxMessageSize 200
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam BoxPadding 10

actor "Admin / User" as Browser
actor "Discord User" as DUser

node "Frontend Dashboard\n(React + Tanstack)" as FE
node "NestJS API Server\n(BFF & Webhooks)" as API
node "NestJS Worker Microservice\n(Heavy Lifting)" as Worker
node "Discord Bot\n(Discord.js)" as Bot

database "PostgreSQL\n(Persistent Data, Queues & Cache)" as DB

cloud "GitHub API / Webhooks" as GitHub
cloud "Discord API" as Discord

Browser <--> FE : View Dashboard / Leaderboards
FE <--> API : REST (Tanstack Query)

GitHub --> API : Webhook Events (PRs, Commits)
API --> DB : Enqueue Event Job (Table)
DB <--> Worker : Dequeue & Process Job (SKIP LOCKED)

Worker --> DB : Update User XP, Stats & Leaderboard
Worker --> Bot : IPC / Event: Send PDF or Notification

Bot <--> Discord : Commands & Messages
DUser <--> Discord : Interact with Bot
API <--> DB : Admin Queries / Dashboard Stats

@enduml